      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not just a body we were made,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But body, soul, and spirit too;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The inmost part the spirit is"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To contact God and Him pursue."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just as we need the earthly food"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our body's need to satisfy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We need the food for spirit too—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thyself, Thy Word, its true supply."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou art the Spirit, and Thy Word"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy very Self expressed doth make;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, it is Spirit as Thyself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Which by our spirit we must take."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, to receive Thy Word is not"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To read it only with our eyes"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And understand it in our mind,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But 'tis the spirit's exercise."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy Word in spirit we must eat"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to our inmost part receive;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "'Tis by our spirit's exercise"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To pray with what our minds perceive."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy Word remaining in our mind"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is only knowledge burdensome,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But when it to the spirit goes"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then life and spirit it becomes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "'Tis only when our spirit acts"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To take Thy Word and contact Thee,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We truly feed upon Thy Word"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And touch Thyself most inwardly."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, teach us how to exercise"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our spirit when Thy Word we read;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then will our spirit nourished be"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As thus upon Thyself we feed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "9"
    }
  ],
